    "The discussion of blockchain technology's incorporation into large language models necessitates a corresponding exploration into the implications of various terms and definitions found at that intersection.",
    "For example, due to the rapid emergence of LLMs, there exists an absence of consensus in describing common phenomena concerning LLM safety and security.",
    "To ameliorate this effect, we take care to stress opposing, but related, definitions of safety found within many different works in Table 2.",
    "In light of these distinctions, we offer two formal definitions of security and safety in order to contextualize these differing but similar areas of research.",
    "These definitions will also serve to highlight where particular blockchain technologies could be applied in their respective domains, and focus research efforts."
